msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/date"
msgid "8th October, 1944 · Tornio, Finno-Swedish border"
msgstr "8 de octubre de 1944 - Tornio, frontera finosueca"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/men"
msgid "You lost all your men!"
msgstr "¡Has perdido a todos tus hombres!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/name"
msgid "The Bridge Too Far"
msgstr "El puente lejano"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/name_big"
msgid "The Bridge Too Far"
msgstr "El puente lejano"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/timer"
msgid "Time until enemy arrival:"
msgstr "Tiempo hasta la llegada del enemigo:"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/story"
msgid " October, 1944. The armistice with the Soviet Union was signed a few weeks ago, and because of that, Finland has to break diplomatic ties with Germany and expel any German soldiers from Finland. The “Lapland war” begins. Parts of 3rd Division are shipped to Tornio, a port on the Swedish border, with reinforcements to follow soon after. At Tornio, they surprise the German garrison and drive them out of the town. Soon after, more elements of the 3rd division are supposed to arrive.\n\n In this mission, you lead the initial landing party, commanding JR 11. You need to set up a perimeter east of Tornio. Expect Kampfgruppe Kraeutler to counterattack from the east, as they will definitely need the Liakanjoki bridge to get to Tornio, and it’s up to you to defend the bridge against your former allies. Set up a defensive line quickly, and hold the bridge until the rest of the division and the tanks arrive."
msgstr ""
"Octubre de 1944. El armisticio con la Unión Soviética se firmó \n"
"\n"
"hace unas semanas, y debido a eso, Finlandia tiene que \n"
"\n"
"romper los lazos diplomáticos con Alemania y expulsar a los soldados "
"alemanes \n"
"\n"
"de Finlandia.  \n"
"\n"
"Comienza la \"guerra de Laponia\". \n"
"\n"
"Partes de la 3ª División son enviadas a Tornio, un puerto en \n"
"\n"
"de la frontera sueca, con refuerzos que le seguirán poco después.  \n"
"\n"
"En Tornio, sorprenden a la guarnición alemana y la expulsan \n"
"\n"
"de la ciudad. Poco después, más elementos de la \n"
"\n"
"3ª división deben llegar. \n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"En esta misión, diriges el grupo de desembarco inicial, \n"
"\n"
"al mando del JR 11. Tienes que establecer un perímetro \n"
"\n"
"al este de Tornio. \n"
"\n"
"Espera que el Kampfgruppe Kraeutler contraataque desde el este, \n"
"\n"
"ya que definitivamente necesitarán el puente Liakanjoki \n"
"\n"
"para llegar a Tornio, y depende de ti defender \n"
"\n"
"el puente contra tus antiguos aliados. \n"
"\n"
"Establece una línea defensiva rápidamente, y mantén el puente \n"
"\n"
"hasta que el resto de la división y los tanques lleguen."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Great job! The Germans are now hurrying along the route north, to escape to "
"Norway. From this moment on, it will be like a walk in the park compared to "
"what we’ve been through since 1939. We’ll be home before Christmas, and by "
"then the war will be over for Finland. Congratulations on a campaign well "
"fought and a victory well earned!"
msgstr ""
"¡Gran trabajo! Los alemanes están ahora apurando la ruta hacia el norte, "
"para escapar a Noruega. A partir de este momento, será como un paseo en el "
"parque en comparación con lo que hemos pasado desde 1939. Estaremos en casa "
"antes de Navidad, y para entonces la guerra habrá terminado para Finlandia. "
"¡Felicidades por una campaña bien luchada y una victoria bien merecida!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This was our chance to live up to the commitment we made to the Soviets, and "
"if they think we’ve failed, they will invade once more - and it won’t be "
"long. Right now, the Germans can take their sweet time to redeploy their "
"troops, and it will be up to us to fend off the red army again."
msgstr ""
"Esta era nuestra oportunidad de cumplir el compromiso que adquirimos con los "
"soviéticos, y si creen que hemos fracasado, nos invadirán una vez más, y no "
"tardarán en hacerlo. En este momento, los alemanes pueden tomarse su tiempo "
"para redesplegar sus tropas, y dependerá de nosotros volver a rechazar al "
"ejército rojo."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/narrator/officer/01"
msgid ""
"Jaegers! Today we have a mission for you of great importance! The fate of "
"the country is in your hands!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jaegers! ¡Hoy tenemos una misión para vosotros de gran importancia! ¡El "
"destino del país está en vuestras manos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/narrator/officer/02"
msgid ""
"The bridge in front of us is of great value to the Germans. They want it "
"because it gives access to the shortest route to Norway."
msgstr ""
"El puente frente a nosotros es de gran valor para los alemanes. Lo quieren "
"porque da acceso a la ruta más corta a Noruega."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/narrator/officer/03"
msgid ""
"I need you to seize the control of that bridge and eliminate the enemy "
"garrison! You're the finest our army has to offer - show us what you're made "
"of!"
msgstr ""
"¡Necesito que tomes el control de ese puente y elimines la guarnición "
"enemiga! Sois lo mejor que tiene nuestro ejército, ¡mostradnos de qué estáis "
"hechos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/narrator/officer/04"
msgid "That's it, men! The bridge is ours. "
msgstr "¡Eso es soldados! El puente es nuestro. "

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/narrator/officer/05"
msgid ""
"The enemy still remains in the nearby settlement, it's necessary you drive "
"them out of there and secure a solid bridgehead."
msgstr ""
"El enemigo aún permanece en el asentamiento cercano, es necesario que los "
"expulses de allí y asegures una sólida cabeza de puente."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/narrator/officer/06"
msgid ""
"Soldiers! The enemy has been driven out but their offensive capability is "
"still extant. You are to fortify the bridgehead and prepare for any possible "
"enemy attacks!"
msgstr ""
"¡Soldados! El enemigo ha sido expulsado, pero su capacidad ofensiva sigue "
"existiendo. ¡Debes fortificar la cabeza de puente y prepararte para "
"cualquier posible ataque enemigo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/narrator/officer/07"
msgid ""
"Listen up, astoveri! Intelligence has reported that the German battle group "
"in the area includes Panzer Battalion 211. Expect an attack with their "
"armour, even if they're just some old captured French tanks. Scavenge as "
"many Anti-tank weapons as possible, and prepare for the enemy attack."
msgstr ""
"¡Escuchen, astoveri! Inteligencia ha informado que el grupo de batalla "
"alemán en la zona incluye el Batallón Panzer 211. Se espera un ataque con su "
"blindaje, aunque sólo sean algunos viejos tanques franceses capturados. "
"Recojed todas las armas antitanque posibles y preparaos para el ataque "
"enemigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/narrator/officer/08"
msgid ""
"Congratulations, soldiers. Your courage and sacrifice are second to none. "
msgstr "Enhorabuena, soldados. Vuestro valor y sacrificio son insuperables. "

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/place"
msgid "11th Jaeger Regiment"
msgstr "11º Regimiento Jaeger"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/task1"
msgid "Secure the bridge"
msgstr "Asegura el puente"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/task2"
msgid "Drive the enemy out of the settlement"
msgstr "Expulsa al enemigo del asentamiento"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/task3"
msgid ""
"Resupply your forces and prepare for the arrival of Kampfgruppe Krautler"
msgstr ""
"Reabastece tus fuerzas y prepárate para la llegada del Kampfgruppe Krautler"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1944_10_tornio/task4"
msgid ""
"Destroy the German column and do not let them get away across the bridge."
msgstr "Destruye la columna alemana y no dejes que se escapen por el puente."
